   - Dimensions: 3.97m (X) × 5.00m (Z)
   - X: 10.46 → 14.43
   - Z: 0 → 5.00

6. **[b]Kitchen (Cuisine)[/b]**: `(10.46, 3.97)`
   - Dimensions: 6.249m (X) × 4.50m (Z)
