   - Z: `[0, 2.00]` vs `[2.00, 5.97]` → No overlap (touch at Z=2.00) ✅
   - **Result**: No overlap (share wall at Z=2.00) ✅

4. **[b]Dining Room vs Kitchen[/b]**:
